data.description: Conveniently located near FSU or TCC! Wonderful 4BR/2 bath home with big front yard, additional concrete pad for your boat or RV inside the large fenced backyard with patio. Freshly painted inside and out with new LVP flooring.  Open kitchen to the Dining/Family Rm area.  Conveniently located in the center of town with close access to everything.  Lots of parking and single car garage.  Front entrance has a wheel chair ramp for easy access. 2013 Roof and 2023 HVAC
